# Sample crontab entries for agentry — third M8 trigger class.
#
# Install with `crontab -e` and paste the relevant lines. ZERO orchestrator
# code: the OS cron daemon runs `orchestrator submit` at the scheduled time.
# The orchestrator only sees a new brief on `agentry:briefs`.
#
# Env the cron shell needs:
#   AGENTRY_REDIS__URL (or a helper script that sources ~/.config/agentry/redis.password)
# For simplicity we source the profile dot-file and trust that it sets
# AGENTRY_REDIS__URL — the figment config loader will pick it up either
# via env or via ~/.config/agentry/agentry.toml.

# Morning plan: 09:00 Mon-Fri, kick off qbot-core daily steward.
# 0 9 * * MON-FRI  . $HOME/.profile; /var/mnt/workspaces/agentry/target/release/orchestrator submit /var/mnt/workspaces/agentry/examples/verify-M0.json >> /var/log/agentry-cron.log 2>&1

# Hourly idempotence ping (echo brief; cheap heartbeat).
# 0 * * * * . $HOME/.profile; /var/mnt/workspaces/agentry/target/release/orchestrator submit /var/mnt/workspaces/agentry/examples/verify-M0.json >> /var/log/agentry-cron.log 2>&1
